{"tid":2031610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"24/5 獨立思考","createTime":"2020-05-23T13:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T02:34:53.000Z","uid":169262,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6ce7879160f52d0e8a41f3cda874522ba1cf7942","tid":2031610,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:38:19.000Z","msg":"求下你地 <br />\n唔好睇到多post叫出  又好多正評<br />\n就衝出去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">獨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">立</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">思</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">考</span></span><br />\n<br />\n每次行動要評估風險<br />\n預測對家戰術<br />\n為自己set deadline 唔死留 屋企要人<br />\n諗定逃生出口<br />\n <br />\n我諗聽日連起步都難<br />\n如果無計 咪即唱雞 和你shop <br />\n一樣比到國際間知香港人未放棄<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚再係旺角開花 </span>"},{"pid":"ead6549f0904162be97f4ad45f37a6ad74e0b6a3","tid":2031610,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"0"},{"pid":"d8497505315b5bf482161dc93d9c441b174bbf80","tid":2031610,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:39:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ed6818e0c2b11932bf6b400c6f86dddf60a1ffe6","tid":2031610,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5548f2b3931a64b144a04b0cce5b6837f2d450a4","tid":2031610,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adb07f340338c34dd5e7ef2fed0a12d23b6d5ca5","tid":2031610,"uid":135890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:40:46.000Z","msg":"順手諗吓poly點解咁血腥 ？<br />\n油麻地點解人踩人？"},{"pid":"dea8f3d56d5e353060f3564321e6844f59299665","tid":2031610,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c